  "body": "- [x] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nWhen I execute truffle serve, it says \"Cannot get /\" in the browser\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nTruffle compile, migrate, then serve. App directory structure: \r\napp/\r\n    --javascripts/\r\n    --stylesheets/\r\n    --index.html\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nServe the static webpage.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nOnce visited in the browser, it prints \"Cannot get /\"\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Ubuntu 16.04\r\n* Truffle version: 3.2.1\r\n* Ethereum client: testrpc\r\n* node version: 8.1.4\r\n* npm version: 5.3.0\r\n",
